    <section name="Ace Workspace Maven Repository">
       <p>It is often more convient to access the latest dependencies from a Maven Repository rather than requiring the developer
         to continually checkout and compile the latest sources. The 
         <a href="https://mgr.servers.aceworkspace.net/apps/ace_archiva/archiva/repository/ace_releases">Ace Workspace Maven Release repository</a> and the 
         <a href="https://mgr.servers.aceworkspace.net/apps/ace_archiva/archiva/repository/ace_snapshots">Ace Workspace Maven Snapshot repository</a>
         is available for this purpose. 
       To allow maven to access the repository, add the following to your settings.xml file:</p>
      <source>
        <pre>
          &lt;profiles&gt;
            &lt;profile&gt;
              &lt;activation&gt;
                &lt;activeByDefault&gt;true&lt;/activeByDefault&gt;
              &lt;/activation&gt;
              &lt;repositories&gt;
                &lt;repository&gt;
                  &lt;id&gt;ace.snapshots&lt;/id&gt;
                  &lt;name&gt;ace snapshot repository&lt;/name&gt;
                  &lt;url&gt;https://mgr.servers.aceworkspace.net/apps/ace_archiva/archiva/repository/ace_snapshots&lt;/url&gt;
                &lt;/repository&gt;
                &lt;repository&gt;
                  &lt;id&gt;ace.releases&lt;/id&gt;
                  &lt;name&gt;ace releases repository&lt;/name&gt;
                  &lt;url&gt;https://mgr.servers.aceworkspace.net/apps/ace_archiva/archiva/repository/ace_releases&lt;/url&gt;
                &lt;/repository&gt;
                &lt;/repositories&gt;
            &lt;/profile&gt;
          &lt;/profiles&gt;
        </pre>
      </source>
      
      <!-- Within sections, any XHTML can be used -->
    </section>
